      Sets the stream loader context.
      The context will be used by all the concatenated routines until changed.
      If null it will cause the next routines to employ the configured runner instead of an Android loader.

      • withLoaders

        @NotNull
public com.github.dm.jrt.android.core.config.LoaderConfiguration.Builder<? extends LoaderStreamChannel<OUT>> withLoaders()
        Description copied from interface: LoaderStreamChannel
        Gets the loader configuration builder related only to the next concatenated routine instance. Any further addition to the chain will retain only the stream configuration.
        Only the options set in this configuration (that is, the ones with a value different from the default) will override the stream ones.

        Note that the configuration builder will be initialized with the current configuration for the next routine.

        Specified by:
